
= "Here we describe the Governance of [[OSE Europe]]."

URL = http://opensourceecology.org/wiki/OSE_Europe/Open_Governance

OSE Europe is an open, dynamic, self-organizing group of people implementing the OSE Europe Mission: The creation of an open society, where everybody's needs are met, and where everybody has access to information, material productivity, and just governance systems - such that human creativity is unleashed, for all people. 


